The type of this extension is 0x0001. The value of this extension is as follows:

```
struct {
   uint64 time_precision; // granularity of the timestamp
   uint64 time; // timestamp at which the token expires, current UNIX time in seconds divided by time_precision
} ExpirationTimestmap;
```

The type of this extension is 0xTODO. The value of this extension is as follows:

```
struct {
   opaque geo_hint<0..2^8-1>; // A string like "US,US-AL,Alabaster"
} GeoHint;
```

Or, alternatively, something like:

```
struct {
   opaque country<0..2^8-1>; // A string like "US"
   opaque region<0..2^8-1>; // A string like "US-AL"
   opaque city<0..2^8-1>; // A string like "Alabaster"
} Geo;
```

